git branch -M main
git remote add origin https://github.com/GridLens/gridlens-energy.git
git push -u origin main</pre>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Enter credentials:</strong> Username: <code>GridLens</code>, Password: your GitHub token</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
